### 8. Update Cargo.toml Test Configuration

**Priority:** HIGH - Enable test filtering
**Estimate:** 15 minutes

**Actions:**
Add test configuration to support running tests by type:

```toml
# In rust/Cargo.toml

# Enable test discovery in subdirectories
[[test]]
name = "unit_tests"
path = "tests/unit/mod.rs"
test = true

[[test]]
name = "integration_tests"
path = "tests/integration/mod.rs"
test = true

[[test]]
name = "e2e_tests"
path = "tests/e2e/mod.rs"
test = true

[[test]]
name = "property_tests"
path = "tests/property/mod.rs"
test = true

[[test]]
name = "performance_tests"
path = "tests/performance/mod.rs"
test = true
```

**Note:** Each directory will need a `mod.rs` file to act as the test root.

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] Can run `cargo test --test unit_tests`
- [ ] Can run `cargo test --test integration_tests`
- [ ] Can run `cargo test --test e2e_tests`
- [ ] Can run `cargo test --test property_tests`
- [ ] Can run `cargo test --test performance_tests`

---

### 9. Create mod.rs Files for Each Test Category

**Priority:** HIGH - Required for Cargo test discovery
**Estimate:** 20 minutes

Create `mod.rs` in each test category directory to enable Cargo's test discovery:

**Files to Create:**

1. `tests/unit/mod.rs`

```rust
// Unit tests - fast, no I/O

pub mod common;
pub mod domain;
pub mod application;
pub mod infrastructure;
```

1. `tests/integration/mod.rs`

```rust
// Integration tests - DB + storage

#[path = "../common/mod.rs"]
mod common;

pub mod use_cases;
pub mod repositories;
pub mod storage;
```

1. `tests/e2e/mod.rs`

```rust
// End-to-end tests - full API

#[path = "../common/mod.rs"]
mod common;

pub mod api;
pub mod security;
```

1. `tests/property/mod.rs`

```rust
// Property-based tests

#[path = "../common/mod.rs"]
mod common;

pub mod domain;
```

1. `tests/performance/mod.rs`

```rust
// Performance regression guards

#[path = "../common/mod.rs"]
mod common;

mod regression_guards;
```

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] All mod.rs files created
- [ ] Each references common utilities appropriately
- [ ] Modules compile without errors

---

### 10. Update GitHub Actions CI

**Priority:** MEDIUM - Ensure CI runs all test types
**Estimate:** 15 minutes

**Current CI:** Likely runs `cargo test` (all tests together)

**Proposed Changes:**
Run tests by category for better visibility and parallelization:

```yaml
- name: Run unit tests
  run: cargo test --test unit_tests

- name: Run integration tests
  run: cargo test --test integration_tests

- name: Run E2E tests
  run: cargo test --test e2e_tests

- name: Run property tests
  run: cargo test --test property_tests

- name: Run performance tests
  run: cargo test --test performance_tests
```

**File to Update:** `.github/workflows/rust.yml` (or similar)

**Acceptance Criteria:**

- [ ] CI runs each test category separately
- [ ] CI shows which test category failed (if any)
- [ ] Total CI time comparable or faster (due to parallelization)

